Package org.ejbca.core.ejb.config

Class ScepConfigurationCache

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ejbca.core.ejb.config.ScepConfigurationCache
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ConfigurationCache
    public final class ScepConfigurationCache
extends Object
implements ConfigurationCache
    Class Holding cache variable for SCEP configuration. Needed because EJB spec does not allow volatile, non-final fields in session beans. This is a trivial cache, too trivial, it needs manual handling of setting the cache variable, this class does not keep track on if the cache variable is null or not, the using class must ensure that it does not try to use a null value. Only the method "needsUpdate will return true of the cache variable is null.
    Version:
